These are the commands I understand:

	**!slime**
		Show your slime score. Mention a user to see their score instead.

	**!mine**
		Mine for slime.

		*Used only in #the-mines.*
		*Awards 20 slime.*
		*Flags you for PvP combat for 3 minutes.*

	**!enlist**
		Join the Rowdy Fuckers or the Cop Killers (if you have enough slime).
		
	**!shoot** *@username*
		Shoot the mentioned player, dealing damage based on your slime level
		and potentially killing them.
		
		*Used only in the #combat-zone.*
		*5 second cooldown.*
		*Flags you for PvP combat for 10 minutes.*

	**!equip** *weapon*
		Equip a weapon to use against your foes.

		*Used only in #the-dojo.*

	**!spar** *@username*
		Practice fighting with the targeted player of your faction.
		The weaker player gains slime.

		*Used only in #the-dojo.*
		*10 minute cooldown.*
		*Flags you for PvP combat for 10 minutes.*

	**!revive**
		Bring yourself back from the dead.

		*Used only in #the-sewers.*

	**!haunt** *@username*
		Haunt a living player from beyond the grave, costing them slime.

		*Used only when dead.*
		*10 minute cooldown.*

	**!slimecoin**
		See how much SlimeCoin you have.

	**!exchangerate**
		See the current exchange rate of slimes per slime credit.

**Used only in the #slime-stock-exchange:**
	**!invest** #
		Invest some slime in the market! You exchange slime for SlimeCoin
		at the current exchange rate, plus a 5% brokerage fee.

		*20 minute cooldown shared with !withdraw.*

	**!withdraw** #
		Cash in your SlimeCoin for cold, wet slime!

		*20 minute cooldown shared with !invest.*
		*Flags you for PvP combat for 3 minutes.*

**Used only in the #slime-casino:**
	**!drink**
		Clears you of all mining-induced fatigue.

	**!slimeslots**
		Play the slime slot machine!

		*Costs 100 slime.*

	**!slimecraps** #
		Toss the dice! Wager some number of slimes and win big.

	**!slimepachinko**
		Drop some balls in the slime pachinko machine!

		*Costs 500 slime.*
